OL,5, Nicola Sturgeon has defended plans to  
OL,6, cut the bottom off some school         
OL,7, classroom doors to improve ventilation 
OL,8, as "basic common sense".               
OL,10,FCouncils have been given #5m of funding
OL,11,Fto improve air flow in around 2,000    
OL,12,Fclassrooms to slow the spread of Covid.
OL,14,FAs well as installing filters and fans,
OL,15,F#300,000 was earmarked to "undercut"   
OL,16,Fdoors to improve airflow.              
OL,18,FOpposition parties said was a "lazy    
OL,19,Fsolution" which could raise safety     
OL,20,Fconcerns, including from risk of fire. 
